content:
Microsoft.VisualBasic.MyServices.Internal Namespace

Definition

The Microsoft.VisualBasic.MyServices.Internal namespace contains internal-use only types that support My in Visual Basic.

In this Article

Classes

ContextValue<T>

This class supports My in Visual Basic.

Remarks

For more information about My in Visual Basic, see Development with My.
